  </aside>

  <main class="main">

    <article class="paper">

      <div class="hero">
        <img src="/channellogo.jpg" alt="Caaligo Main Logo" class="hero-logo" />
        <p class="label">CAALIGO</p>

        <h2>Minecraft Creator</h2>

        <p>
          Exploring Minecraft's forgotten history,
          strange discoveries, mods, and stories.
        </p>
      </div>

      <hr />

      <section>
        <h3>Latest Videos</h3>

        <div class="video-grid">

          <div class="video-card">
            <iframe
              src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9WrYbEGEaNI"
              title="Playing a Minecraft Version That Never Existed"
              frameborder="0"
              allowfullscreen>
            </iframe>

            <h4>Playing a Minecraft Version That Never Existed</h4>

            <p>
              Exploring the world of Minecraft Obsidian Edition.
            </p>

            <a href="https://youtube.com/watch?v=9WrYbEGEaNI" target="_blank">
              Watch on YouTube
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="video-card">
            <iframe
              src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_kFwQPv4X5A"
              title="Caedes ARG Analysis"
              frameborder="0"
              allowfullscreen>
            </iframe>

            <h4>Caedes ARG Analysis</h4>

            <p>
              Investigating the Minecraft Caedes ARG.
            </p>

            <a href="https://youtube.com/watch?v=_kFwQPv4X5A" target="_blank">
              Watch on YouTube
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="video-card">
            <iframe
              src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4bFueBEvSBo"
              title="Every Mod on the Minecraft Mod Iceberg Explained (Part 2)"
              frameborder="0"
              allowfullscreen>
            </iframe>

            <h4>Every Mod on the Minecraft Mod Iceberg Explained (Part 2)</h4>

            <p>
              Exploring the history, development, and stories behind Minecraft mods.
            </p>

            <a href="https://youtube.com/watch?v=4bFueBEvSBo" target="_blank">
              Watch on YouTube
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </section>

      <section>

        <h3>Featured Project</h3>

        <div class="project">
          
          <img src="/moelogo.png" alt="Minecraft Obsidian Edition Logo" class="moe-logo" />

          <h4>Minecraft Obsidian Edition</h4>

          <p>
            A custom Minecraft project focused on
            recreating the feeling of classic Minecraft
            while building something new.
          </p>

          <ul>
            <li>Custom gameplay experience</li>
            <li>Classic Minecraft atmosphere</li>
            <li>Modern 1.20.1 foundation</li>
            <li>Active development</li>
          </ul>

          <a href="/moe">
            View Project
          </a>

        </div>

      </section>

      <section>

        <h3>Latest Updates</h3>

        <div class="log">

          <small>
            JULY 13, 2026
          </small>

          <h4>
            Obsidian Edition Development Update
          </h4>

          <p>
            New improvements are being made to
            world generation and gameplay.
          </p>

        </div>

        <div class="log">

          <small>
            JULY 01, 2026
          </small>

          <h4>
            Channel Update
          </h4>

          <p>
            Caaligo continues expanding with new
            videos and creative projects.
          </p>

        </div>

      </section>

      <section>

        <h3>About Caaligo</h3>

        <p>
          Caaligo is a Minecraft-focused creator brand
          centered around videos, storytelling,
          modding, and experimental projects.
        </p>

      </section>

    </article>

  </main>

</body>
</html>

<style>
:root {
  --accent: #58c7ff;
  --purple: #8c7cff;
  --paper: #ffffff;
}

body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  background-image: url("/space.jpg");
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  background-attachment: fixed;
}

/* Sidebar */
.sidebar {
  position: fixed;
  width: 280px;
  height: 100vh;
  background: rgba(17,20,38,0.95);
  padding: 35px;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  color: white;
  overflow-y: auto;
}

/* Sidebar Channel Logo */
.channel-logo {
  width: 110px;
  height: 110px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  object-fit: cover;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  border: 2px solid var(--accent);
  box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(88, 199, 255, 0.2);
}

.brand h1 {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 42px;
  letter-spacing: 5px;
}

.brand p {
  color: #b8bfd8;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.search input {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 10px;
  margin: 25px 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  background: #20243b;
  border: 1px solid #333;
  color: white;
}

nav {
  margin-bottom: 35px;
}

nav h3 {
  color: var(--accent);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-size: 13px;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
}

nav a {
  display: block;
  color: #cfd5ed;
  text-decoration: none;
  padding: 8px 0;
}

nav a:hover {
  color: white;
}

/* Main */
.main {
  margin-left: 280px;
  padding: 50px;
  min-height: 100vh;
}

.paper {
  max-width: 850px;
  margin: auto;
  background: var(--paper);
  padding: 55px;
  box-shadow: 0 20px 60px black;
}

.hero {
  text-align: center;
}

/* Hero Center Logo */
.hero-logo {
  width: 150px;
  height: 150px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  object-fit: cover;
  margin: 0 auto 20px auto;
  display: block;
  border: 3px solid var(--accent);
  box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(88, 199, 255, 0.3);
}

.label {
  color: #777;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
}

.hero h2 {
  font-size: 42px;
  margin-top: 10px;
}

.hero p {
  color: #555;
  font-size: 18px;
}

hr {
  border: none;
  border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
  margin: 40px 0;
}

h3 {
  font-size: 24px;
}

/* Grid and iFrame Sizing */
.video-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
  gap: 25px;
}

.video-card {
  background: #f2f4f8;
  padding: 20px;
  border-left: 5px solid var(--accent);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

.video-card iframe {
  width: 100%;
  height: 200px;
  border: none;
  background: #000;
}

.video-card h4 {
  margin: 15px 0 10px 0;
}

.video-card p {
  margin-top: 0;
  flex-grow: 1;
}

.card a,
.video-card a,
.project a {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 10px;
  background: #111426;
  color: white;
  padding: 10px 18px;
  text-decoration: none;
  align-self: flex-start;
}

/* Featured Project & Logo */
.project {
  background: #f2f4f8;
  padding: 25px;
  border-left: 5px solid var(--purple);
}

.moe-logo {
  max-width: 250px;
  height: auto;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  display: block;
}

.project h4 {
  margin-top: 0;
}

.log {
  border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
  padding-left: 20px;
  margin: 25px 0;
}

.log small {
  color: #777;
}

@media(max-width:900px) {
  .sidebar {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }
  .main {
    margin-left: 0;
    padding: 20px;
  }
  .paper {
    padding: 30px;
  }
}
</style>